data.description: Look no further-- You are Home Sweet Home!! This home shows pride in ownership and is move in ready!!  This home has many smart home features such as Simplesafe home security system w/smartlock & 1 camera, Ring video doorbell-non wired, Ecobee smart thermostat, & MyQ smart garage system. The washer, dryer, refrigerator, and microwave convey. All furniture in home is available for purchase.  The home features a gas stove and 3 ceiling fans. The Bathroom has been remodeled with new walk in shower & new shower plumbing by Rebath April 2021.
